715637f-b.text:
West 142nd Street, north side, between Eighth and Brad-
hurst Avenue's, showing the White Rock Baptist Church
at No. 303 and a three story frame dwelling at No. 307.
The other frame buildings that formerly were located
here have been removed. The apartment dwellings at the
left face on Bradhurst Avenue.

June 5, 1940
No's. 1-2

P. L. Sperr
